642
00:55:43,573 --> 00:55:45,734
But your mother...

643
00:55:45,909 --> 00:55:48,537
...she was conflicted.

644
00:55:48,712 --> 00:55:52,341
I'm the one that took her in back
and prepped her for the procedure.

645
00:55:52,515 --> 00:55:56,383
- The abortion?
- Yes, the abortion.

646
00:55:59,422 --> 00:56:03,825
She tried to convince me that she was
making the right decision.

647
00:56:04,694 --> 00:56:08,061
But, you know, she was really trying
to convince herself.

648
00:56:08,898 --> 00:56:11,833
She told me
she didn't even know the fella...

649
00:56:12,669 --> 00:56:16,730
...didn't know his name,
met him at a bar...

650
00:56:17,407 --> 00:56:20,069
...and had a night together
and then he was gone.

651
00:56:23,613 --> 00:56:25,478
I listened.

652
00:56:26,649 --> 00:56:30,745
Listened to her
like I did a hundred girls before her.

653
00:56:30,920 --> 00:56:34,822
Nodded, told her I understood.

654
00:56:38,061 --> 00:56:42,020
For some of those girls,
I was their only friend.

655
00:56:44,100 --> 00:56:46,034
Halfway through...

656
00:56:46,669 --> 00:56:49,661
...well, something
must have gone wrong.

657
00:56:50,740 --> 00:56:52,935
I wish I knew what.

658
00:56:55,612 --> 00:57:00,072
But when I went to see your mother,
she was just awakening...

