00:57:08,458 --> 00:57:09,982
For him.

662
00:57:14,497 --> 00:57:17,728
There were things
that happened there...

663
00:57:18,635 --> 00:57:22,628
...terrible things,
things they had me do.

664
00:57:26,176 --> 00:57:31,443
When you hear something
enough times...

665
00:57:32,816 --> 00:57:35,751
...somehow you start to believe it.

666
00:57:36,853 --> 00:57:40,084
It was tissue,
that's what they told us.

667
00:57:40,757 --> 00:57:45,694
It was tissue that couldn't survive,
non-viable tissue.

668
00:57:51,835 --> 00:57:55,168
Your mother came back
the next day.

669
00:57:55,538 --> 00:57:58,029
