688
00:59:16,219 --> 00:59:18,813
And he was just...

689
00:59:23,159 --> 00:59:25,627
I saw him shaking there.

690
00:59:29,232 --> 00:59:31,723
I saw the pain.

691
00:59:35,138 --> 00:59:37,766
And I didn't see no tissue.

692
00:59:39,876 --> 00:59:42,709
I just saw the face of a child.

693
00:59:47,684 --> 00:59:50,881
But you were the big surprise.

694
00:59:51,888 --> 00:59:54,755
Nobody knew about you,
not even your mother.

695
00:59:54,924 --> 00:59:59,122
And you came out, big eyes...

696
01:00:00,229 --> 01:00:03,198
...just beautiful.

697
01:00:18,915 --> 01:00:22,180
I never went back to that clinic.

698
01:00:26,356 --> 01:00:29,052
