699
01:00:29,225 --> 01:00:30,852
Was this mine?

700
01:00:31,628 --> 01:00:32,617
Your mother's.

701
01:00:32,795 --> 01:00:35,958
She gave it to me
when she left the hospital.

702
01:00:36,132 --> 01:00:37,997
And then she just left.

703
01:00:38,167 --> 01:00:42,126
They looked for her, but she changed
